Some mages such as {{champion:45}}, {{champion:1}}   and {{champion:134}} should be able to 1v1 an assassin, but mages like {{champion:101}}, {{champion:69}} {{champion:115}} and {{champion:99}} should have  more trouble, although I believe Lux can still 1v1 Assassins nearly as easy as {{champion:45}}, {{champion:1}}  and {{champion:134}}
